619
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:02,320
 i on je plaćao sve u kruhovima,

620
00:35:02,420 --> 00:35:03,220
 to je bila jedna baluta.

621
00:35:03,220 --> 00:35:06,000
 Znači, on je bio vlasnik žita

622
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,480
 i on je dodjeljivao količinu kruhova

623
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,560
 ili vrčeva piva ljudima.

624
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:11,080
 Ja gledam, to je, misli se i u ovu Egiptu,

625
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:12,380
 to je već ustvareni,

626
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:12,840
 u stvari,

627
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:16,800
 ideal, univerzno tenilnog dohodka,

628
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:17,980
 ali ono što Klaus Schwab kaže,

629
00:35:17,980 --> 00:35:19,100
 nećete imati ništa.

630
00:35:19,100 --> 00:35:19,980
 I bit ćete sretni.

631
00:35:19,980 --> 00:35:21,780
 Sretni je u Egipću, oni stari su pravi bili takvi.

632
00:35:21,780 --> 00:35:22,720
 U njih nije bilo poreza.

633
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:25,200
 Ali zato niko nije imao ništa.

634
00:35:25,200 --> 00:35:26,200
 Da nije bilo nikak nekako poreza.

635
00:35:26,200 --> 00:35:27,640
 E, a kad si već sad spomenuo tu,

636
00:35:27,640 --> 00:35:28,960
 i ja sam i spomenula uvodu,

637
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,460
 nećete imati ništa i bit ćete sretni,

638
00:35:30,460 --> 00:35:32,060
 misliš da ljudi to razumiju,

639
00:35:32,060 --> 00:35:34,340
 da razumiju o čemu je riječ,

640
00:35:34,340 --> 00:35:36,440
 nekakav cilj je postignut,

641
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:39,120
 odnosno zadan sa 2030. godinom,

642
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:41,000
 a sve opet za naše dobro.

643
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,860
 Stalno nam se ponavlja ta mantra,

644
00:35:42,860 --> 00:35:44,060
 to je za vaše dobro.

645
00:35:44,060 --> 00:35:45,960
 Kad mi neko kaže da je nešto za moje dobro,

646
00:35:45,960 --> 00:35:48,500
 ne znam, odlaka mi se pale sve antene na glavi,

647
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:52,500
 ali neki ljudi tu priču gutaju.

648
00:35:52,500 --> 00:35:54,900
 Rečemo za naše dobro priča,

649
00:35:55,180 --> 00:35:56,240
 čekaj malo,

650
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:57,560
 nova viruse i ljudi,

651
00:35:57,560 --> 00:35:59,420
 tu je bilo puno stvari

652
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:01,080
 koje si zapisao i zabilježio.

653
00:36:01,080 --> 00:36:02,560
 Pa to bi još pransko mreza pred očima.

654
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:04,400
 Tako je, radi se o dnevniku korone,

655
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:06,960
 od kada je počela korona do 2021. godine.

656
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,860
 Sve ono što si tu zapisao,

657
00:36:08,860 --> 00:36:09,880
