 koju ljudi kao luče,

726
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:08,260
 ali naravno prvo je trebalo

727
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:09,220
 jedan dobri plin,

728
00:38:09,220 --> 00:38:10,260
 zdravi plin,

729
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:11,340
 korisni plin,

730
00:38:11,340 --> 00:38:12,920
 proglasi neprijateljem.

731
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,000
 Sad svi anticovi,

732
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:14,900
 pa šta fali CO2?

733
00:38:14,900 --> 00:38:16,400
 Čim CO2 ima više,

734
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,060
 biljke su veće.

735
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:18,700
 Pa to se radi u svakom stakleniku.

736
00:38:18,700 --> 00:38:20,160
 Znači, osim toga,

737
00:38:20,160 --> 00:38:20,620
 CO2,

738
00:38:20,620 --> 00:38:22,260
 ja mislim,

739
00:38:22,260 --> 00:38:23,460
 CO2 ima svoje kruženje

740
00:38:23,460 --> 00:38:24,100
 i u principu

741
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:25,240
 CO2 nije čak ni ključni...

742
00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:26,580
 Mislim, to smo učili u školi.

743
00:38:26,580 --> 00:38:28,540
 CO2 čak nije ključni plin staklenika,

744
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:29,460
 nego to vodi na para.

745
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:30,560
 Ali nije sad to bitno.

746
